` (@CategoryInContext.Comma_category_dom.match_1 D C E CC CD CE F G X X (fun x => X) (fun x => X)) = id X `

The left side simplifies to `X` (the first component of the triple), and the right side is `id X` which is also `X`.
So we need to prove `X = X` which is true by reflexivity.

